<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-14452] Unable to configure font or page size on PDF endpoints</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-14452</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This could be related to&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-14284&quot; title=&quot;Configuring endpoint should set properties on endpoint and not configuration object&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CAMEL-14284&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CAMEL-14284&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you try to set the font or pageSize options on a PDF endpoint then you get an NPE. E.g&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;pdf:create?fontSize=6&amp;amp;pageSize=PAGE_SIZE_A5&amp;amp;font=courier&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Probably due to PdfEndpointConfigurer expecting the type to be either PDFont or PDRectangle when its actually trying to deal with a String.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
